# Cenro Desktop has no required environment variables.
#
# Add OpenAI, Anthropic, DeepSeek, GLM, OpenRouter, Groq, or custom-provider
# credentials through Cenro Settings. The desktop app stores keys using the
# operating system's encrypted Electron storage; never commit keys to `.env`.
#
# These optional values only exist for local development of legacy CLI helpers.
# LOCAL_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:11434/v1
# LOCAL_MODEL=qwen2.5-coder:3b
